releaseNotes:
General:
- Upgrade ddl from .net Core to .net Standard
- Unification of dependencies to .net Standard

Improvements Api Controller

- Addition of rules association in vehicles
- Added association of rules in drivers
- Added return of rules in fleets
- Added the GetRules method, new filtering parameters (idVehicle, idDriver, idFleet)
- Added methods for handling OverLimits (downloading, creating and updating)
- Added methods for handling IdentificationsProviders (downloading, creating and updating)
- Added methods for handling Identities (downloading, creating and updating)
- Added methods for managing loyalty accounts (download, create and update)
- Added GetSites method new filtering parameter (idZone)
- Added method for removing rules
- Added methods for obtaining audit log
- Aggregated properties of available to vehicles
- Added properties of available to drivers
- Added methods for handling disputed transactions (downloading, creating and updating)
- Added methods for handling contingency transactions (downloading, creating and updating)
- Added method for obtaining data from the network and its configurations
- Added method for obtaining grouped transactions
- Added methods for downloading sub-accounts
- Added methods for obtaining and updating the configuration of company classifiers
- Added methods for obtaining and creating company classifiers
- Added methods to obtain current account movements
- Added DisputeStatus property to the transaction object obtained in the download
- Added methods for downloading and creating Company Group movements
- Added methods for handling gift card customers (downloading, creating and updating)
- Added methods for handling gift card programs (downloading, creating and updating)
- Added properties of Contract ID, PIN, PAN, Active, IdentificationTypeModel, IdentificationStatus, to vehicle and driver IDs
- DriverId and DriverName properties removed from driver ID
- Added method for updating or changing identification pins


Improvements InterfaceOperations Controller

- Added methods for obtaining and updating GPS data from transactions
- Added program properties to transaction download
- Added to transaction download methods new filtering parameter (idProgram)
- Added terminal property to statement download
- Added methods for downloading gift card transactions
- Added method for downloading consumer card transactions
- Added methods for downloading gift card exceptions
- Added methods for downloading consumer card exceptions
- Added to the transaction and exception get methods a new filtering parameter (dateType) that allows applying the type of date indicated to perform the search
- The date format is updated to support milliseconds
- Added methods for downloading and creating company group movements


New Controller

CommunityOperations:  Added methods for sending community transactions offline
